## Note : my Notmuch configuration set the tag "new" to all new message.

-new +ivaldi.me -- (to:/@ivaldi.me/ or from:/@ivaldi.me/ or cc:/@ivaldi.me/ or bcc:/@ivaldi.me/)
-new +inbox -- folder:ivaldi.me/Inbox and not tag:inbox
-unread -new -inbox +expire -- folder:ivaldi.me/Trash and not tag:expire
-unread -new -inbox +spam -- folder:ivaldi.me/Spam and not tag:span
-unread -new -inbox +sent -- folder:ivaldi.me/Sent and not tag:sent
-unread -new -inbox +archived -- folder:ivaldi.me/Archive and not tag:archived
-new +flagged -- folder:ivaldi.me/Starred and not tag:flagged

## Specific Spam Management

-unread -new -inbox +spam -- XSender:/@salesforce.com/

# Remove the new tag from messages
-new tag:new
